---
---

<section class="py-24 md:py-32 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center mb-20">
      <p class="reveal text-xs font-semibold text-brand-600 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4 font-display">The Problem</p>
      <h2 class="reveal reveal-delay-1 text-3xl md:text-[2.75rem] font-bold tracking-[-0.02em] text-charcoal leading-tight font-display">
        Field services haven't changed in 30&nbsp;years
      </h2>
      <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2 mt-5 text-lg text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed">
        Energy and water companies manage dozens of agency relationships independently.
        Procurement is slow, data is siloed, and there's no cross-industry visibility.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1 group relative p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-100 hover:border-brand-200/60 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-brand-50">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-8 w-12 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-400 to-red-300 rounded-b-full"></div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-red-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3 font-display">Fragmented relationships</h3>
        <p class="text-charcoal-light text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
          Each agency has its own contract, data format, and performance tracking. Internal FTE is spent managing suppliers rather than driving outcomes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 group relative p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-100 hover:border-brand-200/60 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-brand-50">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-8 w-12 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400 to-amber-300 rounded-b-full"></div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-amber-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3 font-display">No cross-industry visibility</h3>
        <p class="text-charcoal-light text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
          Performance data is trapped in silos. There are no industry benchmarks, no best practice sharing, and no way to compare agencies objectively.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3 group relative p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-100 hover:border-brand-200/60 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-brand-50">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-8 w-12 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-orange-300 rounded-b-full"></div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-orange-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3 font-display">Increased data risk</h3>
        <p class="text-charcoal-light text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
          Multiple data interfaces with multiple agencies multiply data breach risk. Each connection is another attack surface in a heavily regulated environment.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
